      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-light leading-tight mb-6">Dental Crown Insurance Coverage</h1>
      <p class="text-white/70 leading-8 text-lg max-w-3xl">Dental crown coverage can be helpful, but it depends on your plan rules, deductible, annual maximum, and whether the insurance company considers the crown eligible.</p>
    </div>
